event = {
	id = 2800000
	random = no

	trigger = {
		OR = {
			AND = {
				month = 0
				NOT = { month = 4 }
				random = 5
			}
			AND = {
				month = 4
				NOT = { month = 8 }
				random = 7
			}
			AND = {
				month = 8
				NOT = { month = 10 }
				random = 10
			}
			month = 11
		}
		control = { province = 12 data = -1 }
		year = 1937
	}

	name = EVT_RES_NAME
	desc = EVT_RES_DESC
	style = 2
	picture = "resources"	
	
	date = { day = 0 month = january year = 1937 }
	offset = 15
	deathdate = { day = 29 month = december year = 1937 }

	action_a = {
		name = "ACTION_NAME_OK"
		command = { type = add_prov_resource which = 12 value = 2 where = metal }
	}
}

	random = no

	trigger = {
		OR = {
			AND = {
				month = 0
				NOT = { month = 4 }
				random = 5
			}
			AND = {
				month = 4
				NOT = { month = 8 }
				random = 7
			}
			AND = {
				month = 8
				NOT = { month = 10 }
				random = 10
			}
			month = 11
		}
		control = { province = 321 data = -1 }
		year = 1937
	}

	name = EVT_RES_NAME
	desc = EVT_RES_DESC
	style = 2
	picture = "resources"	
	
	date = { day = 0 month = january year = 1937 }
	offset = 15
	deathdate = { day = 29 month = december year = 1937 }

	action_a = {
		name = "ACTION_NAME_OK"
		command = { type = add_prov_resource which = 321 value = 1 where = rare_materials }
	}
}

			AND = {
				month = 0
				NOT = { month = 4 }
				random = 5

				month = 4
				NOT = { month = 8 }
				random = 7
			}
			AND = {
				month = 8
				NOT = { month = 10 }
				random = 10
			}
			month = 11
		}
		control = { province = 1813 data = -1 }
		year = 1938
	}

	name = EVT_RES_NAME
	desc = EVT_RES_DESC
	style = 2
	picture = "resources"

	deathdate = { day = 29 month = december year = 1938 }

	random = no

	trigger = {
		OR = {
			AND = {
				month = 0
				NOT = { month = 4 }
				random = 5
			}
			AND = {
				month = 4
				NOT = { month = 8 }
				random = 7
			}
			AND = {
				month = 8
				NOT = { month = 10 }
				random = 10
			}
			month = 11
		}
		control = { province = 1708 data = -1 }
		year = 1940
	}

	name = EVT_RES_NAME
	desc = EVT_RES_DESC
	style = 2
	picture = "resources"	
	
	date = { day = 0 month = january year = 1940 }
	offset = 15
	deathdate = { day = 29 month = december year = 1940 }

	action_a = {
		name = "ACTION_NAME_OK"
		command = { type = add_prov_resource which = 1708 value = 8 where = rare_materials }
	}
}

	random = no

	trigger = {
		OR = {
			AND = {
				month = 0
				NOT = { month = 4 }
				random = 5
			}
			AND = {
				month = 4
				NOT = { month = 8 }
				random = 7
			}
			AND = {
				month = 8
				NOT = { month = 10 }
				random = 10
			}
			month = 11
		}
		control = { province = 1551 data = -1 }
		year = 1941
	}

	name = EVT_RES_NAME
	desc = EVT_RES_DESC
	style = 2
	picture = "resources"	
	
	date = { day = 0 month = january year = 1941 }
	offset = 15
	deathdate = { day = 29 month = december year = 1941 }

		name = "ACTION_NAME_OK"
		command = { type = add_prov_resource which = 1551 value = 1 where = metal }
	}

				NOT = { month = 8 }
				random = 7

				month = 8
				NOT = { month = 10 }
				random = 10
			}
			month = 11
		}
		control = { province = 1886 data = -1 }
		year = 1942
	}
